SmallCircle2S A small circle defined on a 2D Sphere.
 

Package math.geom2s Description

Spherical geometry toolbox.

The package defines a hierarchy of shapes defined on the surface of a sphere. Shapes are organized depending on their dimension: Point2S, Curve2S, Domain2S.
